Hum aapse woh karenge aur ek cheez aap ek kaam kariye bhaiya woh catalog same kar lijiye fir mere ko call karega na sir.
Executive: Nahi sir woh call karne ke liye nahi hai already ek ticket internal bhi sir bol rahe hain ki open kar do external close karwa do na. Yeh bhi to mein bol raha hu internal ticket open kar denge.

Executive: Sir to yeh cheeze hume beech mein aapko bata dena chahiye tha sir ki aapne bola ki hum employees hire kar liye hain iske liye aapko abhi catalog ke liye kuch mat kijiye hamare aapne bola hamare ladke ne kal hamare ladke kar lenge aap tum iska yeh dekhiye sirf review rating ka dekhiye theek hai review rating ka maine.
Customer: Woh Prabhat sir se baat hui thi lekin mere se woh cheeze haan kya sir? kya baat hui hai catalog ke liye.
Executive: Catalog woh to Prabhat sir se jo meri baat aapse hui thi woh yahi cheez hui thi sir aap yaad kijiye na sir.
Customer: Bar bar cheeze repeat nahi karunga mein repeat nahi karunga mein bar bar cheeze meri catalog same kar do then uske baad close hogi usse pehle kuch close nahi hoga bas yeh keh raha hu mein.
Executive: Sir abhi owner kaun hai sir aapke sir owner kaun hai aapki company ke sir? Hello. ID about mein mein hi dekh raha hu bhaiya Udaipur wala.
Customer: Udaipur aap hi dekh rahe hain aur Sumit ji aapke kaun hai sir woh jo aap bol rahe the na Sumit ji Murabad wale. Woh Muradabad ke department hai.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai koi nahi sir theek hai mein ek baar team se baat kar leta hu sir jo bhi cheeze hoga fir mein update karunga theek hai.
Customer: Bilkul bilkul koi close nahi hogi ticket bas yahi kahunga mein aapko hai na.
Executive: Hmm theek hai. Theek hai bhaiya. Okay.
